Property.Name: BodyScript

Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT IdClinicaProfissional, tbc.idProfissional, tbp.ccNome, tbc.cvTaxaProfissional, tbc.cvStatus, tbo.observacao FROM tbClinicaProfissional tbc INNER JOIN tbProfissionais tbp ON tbc.idProfissional = tbp.IdProfissional LEFT JOIN tbObservacoes tbo ON TBC.idObservacao = tbo.IdObservacao WHERE idClinica = @idClinica AND tbc.cvStatus = 1 END

BEGIN
IF @IdClinica = 0 BEGIN SELECT tbc.IdClinica , tbc.ccApelido , tbc.ccRazaoSocial , tbc.ccNomeFantasia , tbc.ccEmail , tbc.cvISS , tbc.cvDescontos , CASE WHEN tbc.cbDescontoVariavel = 1 THEN 'Sim' ELSE 'Não' END cbDescontoVariavel , tbb.ccBanco , ISNULL(tbc.cvPgtoDias,0) cvPgtoDias , tbObs.observacao FROM tbClinicas tbc LEFT JOIN tbBancos tbb ON tbc.idBanco = tbb.IdBanco LEFT JOIN tbObservacoes tbObs ON tbc.idObservacao = tbObs.IdObservacao WHERE tbc.cvStatus = @Status END ELSE BEGIN SELECT tbc.IdClinica , tbc.ccApelido , tbc.ccRazaoSocial , tbc.ccNomeFantasia , tbc.ccEmail , tbc.cvISS , tbc.cvDescontos , CASE WHEN tbc.cbDescontoVariavel = 1 THEN 'Sim' ELSE 'Não' END cbDescontoVariavel , tbb.ccBanco , ISNULL(tbc.cvPgtoDias,0) cvPgtoDias , tbObs.observacao FROM tbClinicas tbc LEFT JOIN tbBancos tbb ON tbc.idBanco = tbb.IdBanco LEFT JOIN tbObservacoes tbObs ON tbc.idObservacao = tbObs.IdObservacao WHERE tbc.cvStatus = @Status AND tbc.IdClinica = @IdClinica END END;
